snippet.title: TURBO OVERKILL - Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1328350/Turbo_Overkill/
Follow development on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/turbo_overkill​​
Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/22xvVZg

Turbo Overkill is a retro cyberpunk FPS where you play as a violent killing machine with a chainsaw for a leg. Coming soon to PC.
